      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Overview"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "This page is to analyze the USS dependencies with SIAL domain BSW software"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Hardware connection"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "In CCU Fusion project, USS is connected to SAIL domain like shown below"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/CCU%20-%20USS%20dependency%20with%20SAIL%20Analysis/image-2024-11-19_14-2-30.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/CCU - USS dependency with SAIL Analysis/image-2024-11-19_14-2-30.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "We will have two Elmos devices connected to SAIL and these two ELMOS have two channel each and each channel connects to 12 USS sensors"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "2 Elmos x 2 channels x 3 sensors = 12 USS sensors"
      ]
    },
